# Terrarium ownership = the path-scoped auto-merge backstop.
#
# A purely-additive PR under specimens/<new-id>/ may auto-merge on green Gate 0
# checks (see .github/workflows/automerge.yml). EVERYTHING ELSE — the pipeline,
# the reviewer registry, generated build records, the signed log — requires a
# first-party (maintainer) review. Branch protection on `main` must require
# CODEOWNERS review for these paths and the `converge` status check for all PRs.
#
# Replace @terrarium-registry/maintainers with the real org/team at repo creation.

*                       @terrarium-registry/maintainers
/.github/               @terrarium-registry/maintainers
/cli/                   @terrarium-registry/maintainers
/src/                   @terrarium-registry/maintainers
/reviewers/             @terrarium-registry/maintainers
/builds/                @terrarium-registry/maintainers
/attestations/          @terrarium-registry/maintainers
/log/                   @terrarium-registry/maintainers
